                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <article>
                    <img class="register-icon" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ironhack-project2/image/upload/v1606392311/project2/farm-icon-removebg-preview_vx1nyg.png" alt="farm">
                    <h3 class="mt-3 how-work">2. Register your farm</h3>
                    <p>Upload a photo, add a short description and all the details of your farm.
                        Don't forget to fill your farm's coordinates if you want to be displayed in our map and be
                        easily found by customers </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <article>
                    <img class="register-icon" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ironhack-project2/image/upload/v1606392311/project2/list-products-removebg-preview_xwmyhr.png" alt="farm products">
