                    <p>Upload a photo, just enter the details of the product, click Submit and instantly your Ad
                        will be displayed.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <article>
                    <img class="account-icon" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ironhack-project2/image/upload/v1606392311/project2/sell-products-removebg-preview_hkkghc.png" alt="sell products">
                    <h3 class="mt-3 how-work">4. Start to sell</h3>
                    <p>Discuss with customers interested in your products about the sale details and close the deal.
                        Selling your farm's products has never been easier.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
